# {{PROJECT_NAME}}

General-purpose R project template.

## Layout

```
{{PROJECT_NAME}}/
├── .gitignore
├── .Rprofile
├── rproject.toml
├── README.md
├── config/
│   └── analysis.yaml
├── R/
│   └── utils.R
├── scripts/
│   └── run_analysis.R
├── data/
├── results/
├── logs/
├── tests/
└── docs/
```

## Quick start

### Interactive
Open the project in RStudio and run:

```r
source("scripts/run_analysis.R")
```

### Command line
```bash
rv sync                          # install packages
rv run                           # run the default script
Rscript scripts/run_analysis.R   # or run directly
```

## Notes

- Manage packages with `rv add` / `rv rm` (declared in `rproject.toml`)
- Put reusable helpers in `R/`
- Keep raw input data in `data/`
- Write outputs to `results/`
